queries.sql: SELECT * FROM mo_movie WHERE `mo_movie`.branch_id = '1' -- AND `mo_movie`.movie_type = 'se' AND mo_movie.movie_active = '1' ORDER BY `mo_movie`.movie_year DESC , `mo_movie`.movie_create DESC

SELECT * FROM mo_movie WHERE `mo_movie`.branch_id = '1' -- AND `mo_movie`.movie_type = 'se' AND mo_movie.movie_active = '1' ORDER BY `mo_movie`.movie_year DESC , `mo_movie`.movie_create DESC LIMIT 0, 20

SELECT * FROM mo_category INNER JOIN mo_moviecate ON mo_moviecate.category_id = mo_category.category_id INNER JOIN mo_movie ON mo_moviecate.movie_id = mo_movie.movie_id WHERE `mo_category`.branch_id = 1 AND mo_movie.movie_active = '1' GROUP BY mo_category.category_id
SELECT movie_year FROM `mo_movie` WHERE branch_id = '1' GROUP BY movie_year ORDER BY movie_year DESC

SELECT mo_category.category_id, mo_category.category_name, GROUP_CONCAT( mo.movie_id, '{-}', REPLACE(mo.movie_thname,'|','/'), '{-}', mo.movie_ratescore, '{-}', mo.movie_view, '{-}', mo.movie_type, '{-}', mo.movie_quality, '{-}', mo.movie_picture SEPARATOR '|' ) AS movie FROM mo_category LEFT JOIN ( SELECT mo_movie.movie_id, mo_movie.movie_thname, mo_movie.movie_picture, mo_movie.movie_type, mo_movie.movie_quality, mo_movie.movie_ratescore, CASE WHEN mo_movie.movie_view IS NULL THEN '0' ELSE mo_movie.movie_view END AS movie_view, mo_moviecate.category_id FROM mo_movie INNER JOIN mo_moviecate ON mo_moviecate.movie_id = mo_movie.movie_id GROUP BY mo_movie.movie_id ORDER BY mo_movie.movie_year desc , mo_movie.movie_id desc ) mo ON mo.category_id = mo_category.category_id WHERE mo_category.branch_id = '1' AND mo.movie_id IS NOT NULL GROUP BY mo_category.category_id ORDER BY count(mo_category.category_id) DESC ;
